Micro Core accepts the following persistence options:

 microcore tce={hda1|sda1}            Specify Restore TCE apps directory
 microcore restore={hda1|sda1|floppy} Specify saved configuration location
 microcore waitusb=X                  Wait X seconds for slow USB devices
 microcore swapfile{=hda1}            Scan or Specify swapfile
 microcore home={hda1|sda1}           Specify persistent home directory
 microcore opt={hda1|sda1}            Specify persistent opt directory
 microcore local={hda1|sda1}          Specify PPI directory or loopback file
 microcore lst=yyy.lst                Load alternate static yyy.lst on boot
 microcore base                       Skip TCE load only the base system
 microcore norestore                  Turn off the automatic restore
 microcore safebackup                 Saves a backup copy (mydatabk.tgz)
 microcore showapps                   Display application names when booting
 
